title: BigFish Games - Mystery Case Files Return to Ravenhearst  FINAL
description:
Mystery Case Files Return to Ravenhearst


Emma`s soul is free. But her ghost has delivered a dire warning: evil 

still lurks in Ravenhearst Manor. Big Fish Games Studios takes you deep 

inside the cursed estate in Mystery Case Files: Return to Ravenhearst 

&trade, the thrilling sequel. Experience Ravenhearst`s spectral halls 

as never before with new immersive adventure-style gameplay and an epic 

original soundtrack. Feel the floorboards creak as you move from room 

to room solving puzzles and seeking out clues in over 150 detailed 

scenes.

The biggest MCF game to date
Dozens of new puzzles
Can you reveal the secret?

Thanx to TAC-CM
